results.advice: Since your banana plant is in the vegetative stage with 15 healthy green leaves, focus on encouraging continued growth and preparing it for the flowering stage. Ensure the plant has high levels of potassium and nitrogen, as these are critical nutrients during this phase. Also, make sure your plant is getting enough water, and that the soil is well-draining.

results.advice: Since your banana plant is in the vegetative stage with 15 healthy green leaves, focus on promoting strong pseudostem and root development. Ensure it gets high levels of potassium and nitrogen. Also, make sure the plant is protected from strong winds and extreme temperature fluctuations (below 15 C or above 35 C).
results.translated_advice: आपली केळीची वनस्पती 15 निरोगी हिरव्या पानांसह वनस्पतिवत् होणार् या अवस्थेत असल्याने मजबूत स्यूडोस्टेम आणि रूट डेव्हलपमेंटला प्रोत्साहन देण्यावर लक्ष केंद्रित करा. याची खात्री करुन घ्या की त्यास पोटॅशियम आणि नायट्रोजनचे उच्च प्रमाण मिळेल. तसेच, हे सुनिश्चित करा की वनस्पती जोरदार वारा आणि तापमान तापमानात चढ -उतार (15 से. च्या खाली किंवा 35 से. पेक्षा जास्त) पासून संरक्षित आहे.
